reviews.reviewText: I like that this muzzle is soft so you dont feel so guilty putting it on your dog. It can rip of they paw at it but they have a replacement policy which is nice and you should always supervise your dog anyway. For the most part though it is durable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Perfect toys, recommend 3-5 year olds
reviews.reviewText: These kept my kids busy for hours. They are larger toys which makes it easy for them to grab and move. each one has a cool feature and different noises. The bus door broke quickly and the top popped off of the garbage truck. This was due to the kids dropping them off the table, so if you have 3-5 year olds these toys would last longer. Overall great playtime toy, but a few only lasted through the weekend with the roughness of play.
